data.title: Ancestors of Carole Joan Deneen
data.text:
Family Links

Spouses/Children:

1. Leo Alfred Cassibo

Carole Joan Deneen

Born: 16 Dec 1931, Loman, Koochiching Co, Minnesota, United States

Marriage (1): Leo Alfred Cassibo on 6 Sep 1949 in Koochiching Co, Minnesota, United States

Died: 13 Mar 2019, Koochiching Co, Minnesota, United States at age 87

Buried: Forest Hill Cemetery, International Falls, Koochiching Co, Minnesota, United States

Research Notes:

Carole J **

OBIT: posted on findagrave, id 197580644

- died at age 87, 13 Mar 2019 - care home in Ranier

- born 16 Dec 1931 in Watrous Twp on Caroline Anderson's farm on Black River Road

- survived by her sons: Bruce, Tim; daughters, Karen (m. Basaraba),

Cheryl (m. Norbury)

- survived by brothers; Dale Deneen, Roger Deneen, and Sisters Leah Rae (m. Kundson)

and Naomi (m. Roste)

From MN birth index, Ancestry; Carole Joan and Leo Alfred Cassibo

Linda Carole Cassibo, b 28 Dec 1950, Koochiching

Karen Ann Cassibo, b 2 Jul 1952, Koochiching

Bruce Leo Cassibo, b 8 Jul 1957, Koochiching

Tim Alan Cassibo, b 28 Jan 1961, Koochiching

Cheryl Lynn Cassibo, 31 Aug 1959, Koochiching

Leo Alfred Cassibo,

OBIT: International Falls Journal; 10 Apr 2012

- died 6 Apr 2012 at Littlefork Care Center, age 81

- born 30 Nov 1930 at International Falls

- worked for Contel phone company; retired in 1990

- preceded parents, brother and sisters, and daughter Linda

- survived by sons, Bruce Cassibo of International Falls, and Tim (April) of Nampa Idaho; daughters, Karen (Ken Basaraba of Fort Frances, ON and Cheryl (Mike Norbury) of Eden Prairie, MN

++ Leo and Carole divorced on 12 Mar 1990 (MN Divorce index, 1970-1995; ancestry)

[https://www.ancestry.com/imageviewer/collections/1081/images/mndiv_0401-0260?pId=304069]

and Leo had remarrid on 23 Dec 1991, Koochiching Co to Carol Mreadman age 51

[MN Marriage Index, 1958-1995, anncestry], but neither of his marriages are noted

in his obit]

-- daughter, Linda Carole Cassibo b 28 Dec 1950 at International Falls

was married on 27 Dec 1969, International Falls to Leon Vernon Engleking, b 11 Oct 1949 at International Falls. They divorced in Sep 1975 after a 1 year separation

[Virginia Divorce Records 1918-2014; ancestry collection]. Divorce degree

finalized on 18 Jun 1976 - that maybe the date. One child, under the age of 18. On the form her "usual residence" was in San Diego, CA - did she move? Or the form says that he was granted divorce and so maybe he had moved, even though his usual residence as noted at Santa Monica, CA ??

- Apparently her death was in CA

some of the above from Ashley Cassibo FT ...

https://www.ancestry.com/family-tree/person/tree/103449690/person/420026207787/facts

Note: there are a number of FTs on Ancestry, by searching Leo Alfred Cassibo

Carole married Leo Alfred Cassibo on 6 Sep 1949 in Koochiching Co, Minnesota, United States. (Leo Alfred Cassibo was born on 30 Nov 1930 in Koochiching Co, Minnesota, United States and died on 10 Apr 2012 in Koochiching Co, Minnesota, United States.)
